name: SEE YOURSELF GROW
description:
As a person who has been in the corporate world for 20 years, Tina knows what it means to climb the corporate ladder, work crazy long hours, commute to work 4 hours a day and miss out on precious moments with my family. January 2019 she had a breakdown in the office, which then lead her to her greatest breakthrough that it was time to focus on achieving her perfect day, instead of chasing after the perfect corporate title. Tina Collura has been coaching and motivating people to live their purpose, achieve balance and focus on all that is good in their lives since 2009. If you can wake up every morning and say to yourself that you are in love with what you are doing - then CONGRATULATIONS! You are part of the 20% of people in this world that are doing what they love!
 However, if you are not part of that 20%, then I want to talk to you about how you can get there.
business_objectives: Accelerate Skill Development and Learning Efficiency
Headline: Are you ready to LEVEL UP in your BUSINESS?
ShortDescription: As a person who has been in the corporate world for 20 years, Tina knows what it means to climb the corporate ladder, work crazy long hours, commute to work 4 hours a day and miss out on precious moments with my family.
enhanced_description: SEE YOURSELF GROW offers personalized coaching services led by Tina Collura, a professional with 20 years of experience in the corporate world. Drawing from her own journey of transitioning from a demanding corporate career, Tina provides personal, professional, and productivity coaching. Launched in 2009, this service aims to help individuals, especially those feeling unfulfilled in their current roles, to 'LEVEL UP in their BUSINESS.' The focus is on achieving personal purpose, work-life balance, and overall well-being, rather than solely chasing corporate titles. Additionally, Tina serves as a motivational speaker, supporting accelerated skill development and learning efficiency.
key_use_cases: Career transition and pathfinding for corporate professionals
Improving work-life balance and personal fulfillment
Providing motivational speaking engagements for organizations
Accelerating skill development and learning efficiency within a corporate context
competitive_advantages: Founder's extensive corporate background (20 years) provides relatable experience and empathy
Focus on holistic personal and professional growth, including purpose and balance, beyond just career advancement
Proven track record of coaching and motivating individuals since 2009
roi_benefits: Enhanced personal and professional skill development
Potential for increased employee retention (implied by fostering fulfillment)
primary_users: Individuals seeking personal and professional growth in their careers
Professionals looking for career transition or purpose
Employees aiming to enhance productivity and achieve better work-life balance
Organizations or companies seeking motivational speakers for their staff development programs
